name: Water Birth of Junkies
description:
The visual of the boy falling into the water interprets the method
water birth which means a person's birth. A person means a boy that so young and falling in drug world. 
It depicts a successful boy
get out of the world of drugs visualized in dark colors. Jellyfish
interpreting the subject that influences the birth process of a person
towards a better world, namely family and friends. Yellow color
means the happiness:
support, love and enthusiasm to become a better person. This work
expected to be able to touch a person's sense to learn from mistakes,
then that mistakes used as a teacher so that in the future
able to self-regulate to become a better person.
